co.cask.coopr.spec

Class Provider

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.cask.coopr.spec.NamedEntity
      • co.cask.coopr.spec.BaseEntity
        • co.cask.coopr.spec.Provider

  • public final class Provider
extends BaseEntity
    Machine providers are instances of some ProviderType like openstack, aws, rackspace, or joyent that can provision machines. Providers are referenced by ImageType and HardwareType.
